<h1><code ng:non-bindable="">jqmButton</code>
<div><span class="hint">directive in module <code ng:non-bindable="">jqm</code>
</span>
</div>
</h1>
<div><h2 id="description">Description</h2>
<div class="description"><div class="jqm-directive-page jqm-directive-jqmbutton-page"><p>Creates a jquery mobile button on the given element.</p>
<p>If created on an anchor <code>&lt;a&gt;</code> tag, the button will be treated as a link button.</p>
</div></div>
<h2 id="usage">Usage</h2>
<div class="usage">as attribute<pre class="prettyprint linenums">&lt;ANY jqm-button="{submit|reset}"
     [icon="{string}"]
     [iconpos="{left|right|top|bottom}"]
     [mini="{boolean}"]
     [inline="{boolean}"]
     [shadow="{boolean}"]
     [corners="{boolean}"]&gt;
   ...
&lt;/ANY&gt;</pre>
<h4 id="usage_parameters">Parameters</h4><table class="variables-matrix table table-bordered table-striped"><thead><tr><th>Param</th><th>Type</th><th>Details</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>jqmButton <div><em>(optional)</em></div></td><td><a href="" class="label type-hint type-hint-submit">submit</a><a href="" class="label type-hint type-hint-reset">reset</a></td><td><div class="jqm-directive-page jqm-directive-jqmbutton-page"><p>The button type - if specified, the button will be treated as an input with the given value as its type. Otherwise, the button will just be a normal button.</p>
</div></td></tr><tr><td>icon <div><em>(optional)</em></div></td><td><a href="" class="label type-hint type-hint-string">string</a></td><td><div class="jqm-directive-page jqm-directive-jqmbutton-page"><p>Defines an icon for the button</p>
</div></td></tr><tr><td>iconpos <div><em>(optional)</em></div></td><td><a href="" class="label type-hint type-hint-left">left</a><a href="" class="label type-hint type-hint-right">right</a><a href="" class="label type-hint type-hint-top">top</a><a href="" class="label type-hint type-hint-bottom">bottom</a></td><td><div class="jqm-directive-page jqm-directive-jqmbutton-page"><p>Defines the Position of the icon, default is &#39;left&#39;</p>
</div></td></tr><tr><td>mini <div><em>(optional)</em></div></td><td><a href="" class="label type-hint type-hint-boolean">boolean</a></td><td><div class="jqm-directive-page jqm-directive-jqmbutton-page"><p>Whether or not to use the mini layout</p>
</div></td></tr><tr><td>inline <div><em>(optional)</em></div></td><td><a href="" class="label type-hint type-hint-boolean">boolean</a></td><td><div class="jqm-directive-page jqm-directive-jqmbutton-page"><p>Whether or not to make the button inline (smaller)</p>
</div></td></tr><tr><td>shadow <div><em>(optional)</em></div></td><td><a href="" class="label type-hint type-hint-boolean">boolean</a></td><td><div class="jqm-directive-page jqm-directive-jqmbutton-page"><p>Whether or not to give the button shadows (default true)</p>
</div></td></tr><tr><td>corners <div><em>(optional)</em></div></td><td><a href="" class="label type-hint type-hint-boolean">boolean</a></td><td><div class="jqm-directive-page jqm-directive-jqmbutton-page"><p>Whether or not to give the button shadows (default true)</p>
</div></td></tr></tbody></table></div>
<h2 id="example">Example</h2>
<div class="example"><div class="jqm-directive-page jqm-directive-jqmbutton-page"><h4 id="example_source">Source</h4>
<div source-edit="jqm" source-edit-deps="angular.js" source-edit-html="index.html" source-edit-css="" source-edit-js="" source-edit-json="" source-edit-unit="" source-edit-scenario=""></div>
<div class="tabbable"><div class="tab-pane" title="index.html">
<pre class="prettyprint linenums" ng-set-text="index.html" ng-html-wrap-loaded="jqm angular.js"></pre>
<script type="text/ng-template" id="index.html">
<div>
  <div jqm-button icon="ui-icon-search" ng-click>Do some search</div>
  <a jqm-button icon="ui-icon-home" data-mini="true" href="#/api" ng-click>Go home, mini!</a>
  <hr />
  <h5 id="example_source_form-with-vertical-group">Form With Vertical Group</h5>
  <form action="http://foobar3000.com/echo" method="GET">
    <div jqm-textinput ng-model="$root.value" ng-init="$root.value='banana'" name="stuff"></div>
    <div jqm-controlgroup>
    <div jqm-button="submit" ng-click icon="ui-icon-check" iconpos="right">Submit to foobar3030.com</div>
    <div jqm-button="reset" ng-click icon="ui-icon-minus" iconpos="right">"reset" it away!</div>
    </div>
  </form>
  <hr />
  <h5 id="example_source_horizontal-group">Horizontal Group</h5>
  <div jqm-controlgroup type="horizontal">
    <div jqm-button ng-click>One</div>
    <div jqm-button ng-click>Two</div>
    <div jqm-button ng-click>Three</div>
  </div>
</div>
</script>
</div>
</div><h4 id="example_demo">Demo</h4>
